           <div class=\"bg fill bg-fill \"><\/div>\n                        <div class=\"overlay\"><\/div>            \n                    <\/div>\n\t\t\n        <div class=\"banner-layers container\">\n            <a class=\"fill\" href=\"Portfolio\"  ><div class=\"fill banner-link\"><\/div><\/a>            \n   <div id=\"text-box-1565559631\" class=\"text-box banner-layer x50 md-x50 lg-x50 y50 md-y50 lg-y50 res-text\">\n              <div data-parallax=\"-3\" data-parallax-fade=\"true\">       <div data-animate=\"fadeInUp\">           <div class=\"text-box-content text dark text-shadow-5\">\n              \n              <div class=\"text-inner text-center\">\n                  \n<p class=\"lead\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp t\u1eeb 2010, <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/\">\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/a> hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ty c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ti\u00ean phong trong nhi\u1ec1u l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c nh\u01b0: \u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 trong b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng, qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng, s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t n\u1ed9i dung lan t\u1ecfa tr\u00ean M\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i&#8230;<\/p>\n<p class=\"lead\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y c\u00e1c h\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng tr\u00ean M\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111a d\u1ea1ng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c. <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/\">\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/a> s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng trong b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cao nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 gi\u00fap doanh nghi\u1ec7p b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng, t\u0103ng doanh thu v\u00e0 l\u1ee3i nhu\u1eadn&#8230;<\/p>\n              <\/div>\n           <\/div>\n       <\/div>       <\/div>              \n<style>\n#text-box-1565559631 .text-inner {\n  padding: 0px 15px 0px 15px;\n}\n#text-box-1565559631 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n#text-box-1565559631 .text-box-content {\n  font-size: 131%;\n}\n@media (min-width:550px) {\n  #text-box-1565559631 {\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n  #text-box-1565559631 .text-box-content {\n    font-size: 100%;\n  }\n}\n<\/style>\n    <\/div>\n \n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n            \n<style>\n#banner-561526210 {\n  padding-top: 100%;\n  background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\n}\n#banner-561526210 .bg.bg-loaded {\n  background-image: url(https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/achaumedia-banner-1.jpg);\n}\n#banner-561526210 .overlay {\n  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.27);\n}\n#banner-561526210 .bg {\n  background-position: 49% 43%;\n}\n#banner-561526210 .ux-shape-divider--top svg {\n  height: 150px;\n  --divider-top-width: 100%;\n}\n#banner-561526210 .ux-shape-divider--bottom svg {\n  height: 150px;\n  --divider-width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n  <\/div>\n\n\n  <div class=\"banner-grid-wrapper\">\n  <div id=\"banner-grid-1693542942\" class=\"banner-grid row row-grid row-collapse row-full-width\" data-packery-options=\"\">\n                      \n<div class=\"col grid-col large-6 grid-col-2-3\" ><div class=\"col-inner\">\n\n  <div class=\"banner has-hover bg-zoom\" id=\"banner-304926602\">\n          <div class=\"banner-inner fill\">\n        <div class=\"banner-bg fill\" >\n            <div class=\"bg fill bg-fill \"><\/div>\n                        <div class=\"overlay\"><\/div>            \n                    <\/div>\n\t\t\n        <div class=\"banner-layers container\">\n            <a class=\"fill\" href=\"Portfolio\"  ><div class=\"fill banner-link\"><\/div><\/a>            \n   <div id=\"text-box-465012743\" class=\"text-box banner-layer x0 md-x0 lg-x0 y50 md-y50 lg-y50 res-text\">\n                     <div data-animate=\"fadeInRight\">           <div class=\"text-box-content text dark text-shadow-5\">\n              \n              <div class=\"text-inner text-left\">\n                  \n<h3>\u00a0<\/h3>\n<h3>\u00a0<\/h3>\n<h3 class=\"uppercase\"><strong>Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"lead\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m 2014, v\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng, \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<p class=\"lead\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn nay v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch l\u0169y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c theo th\u1eddi gian, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb, s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n. \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, chau chu\u1ed1t cho t\u1eebng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c m\u1edbi m\u1ebb v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho m\u1ed7i s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ebb t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 t\u01b0 duy \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ed1t.<\/p>\n<p class=\"lead\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cam k\u1ebft mang t\u1edbi Qu\u00fd v\u1ecb nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t&#8230;<\/p>\n              <\/div>\n           <\/div>\n       <\/div>                     \n<style>\n#text-box-465012743 .text-inner {\n  padding: 0px 15px 0px 15px;\n}\n#text-box-465012743 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n#text-box-465012743 .text-box-content {\n  font-size: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n    <\/div>\n \n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n            \n<style>\n#banner-304926602 {\n  padding-top: 500px;\n}\n#banner-304926602 .bg.bg-loaded {\n  background-image: url(https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/to-chuc-su-kien-1024x682.jpg);\n}\n#banner-304926602 .overlay {\n  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n}\n#banner-304926602 .bg {\n  background-position: 53% 69%;\n}\n#banner-304926602 .ux-shape-divider--top svg {\n  height: 150px;\n  --divider-top-width: 100%;\n}\n#banner-304926602 .ux-shape-divider--bottom svg {\n  height: 150px;\n  --divider-width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n  <\/div>\n\n\n<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"col grid-col large-6 grid-col-1-2\" ><div class=\"col-inner\">\n\n  <div class=\"banner has-hover bg-zoom\" id=\"banner-820236589\">\n          <div class=\"banner-inner fill\">\n        <div class=\"banner-bg fill\" >\n            <div class=\"bg fill bg-fill \"><\/div>\n                        <div class=\"overlay\"><\/div>            \n                    <\/div>\n\t\t\n        <div class=\"banner-layers container\">\n            <a class=\"fill\" href=\"Portfolio\"  ><div class=\"fill banner-link\"><\/div><\/a>            \n   <div id=\"text-box-1728920749\" class=\"text-box banner-layer x50 md-x50 lg-x50 y50 md-y50 lg-y50 res-text\">\n                     <div data-animate=\"fadeInLeft\">           <div class=\"text-box-content text dark text-shadow-5\">\n              \n              <div class=\"text-inner text-right\">\n                  \n<h3 class=\"uppercase\"><strong>th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p \u00c1 CH\u00c2U MEDIA<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"lead\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cTr\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m, tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m\u201d \u2013 Ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p m\u00e0 \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi t\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 Qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<p class=\"lead\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cam k\u1ebft h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i \u00edch v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 y\u00ean t\u00e2m cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. Lu\u00f4n \u201csong h\u00e0nh\u201d c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn \u201cl\u1ee3i \u00edch d\u00e0i l\u00e2u\u201d.<\/p>\n<p class=\"lead\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kim ch\u1ec9 nam trong ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kinh doanh l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c tr\u00ean quan \u0111i\u1ec3m chia s\u1ebb l\u1ee3i \u00edch l\u1eabn nhau. Lu\u00f4n trung th\u1ef1c, c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n              <\/div>\n           <\/div>\n       <\/div>                     \n<style>\n#text-box-1728920749 .text-inner {\n  padding: 0px 15px 0px 15px;\n}\n#text-box-1728920749 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n#text-box-1728920749 .text-box-content {\n  font-size: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n    <\/div>\n \n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n            \n<style>\n#banner-820236589 {\n  padding-top: 500px;\n}\n#banner-820236589 .bg.bg-loaded {\n  background-image: url(https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/su-dam-me.jpg);\n}\n#banner-820236589 .overlay {\n  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.19);\n}\n#banner-820236589 .bg {\n  background-position: 53% 69%;\n}\n#banner-820236589 .ux-shape-divider--top svg {\n  height: 150px;\n  --divider-top-width: 100%;\n}\n#banner-820236589 .ux-shape-divider--bottom svg {\n  height: 150px;\n  --divider-width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n  <\/div>\n\n\n<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"col grid-col large-6 grid-col-1-2\" ><div class=\"col-inner\">\n\n  <div class=\"banner has-hover bg-zoom\" id=\"banner-575302794\">\n          <div class=\"banner-inner fill\">\n        <div class=\"banner-bg fill\" >\n            <div class=\"bg fill bg-fill \"><\/div>\n                        <div class=\"overlay\"><\/div>            \n                    <\/div>\n\t\t\n        <div class=\"banner-layers container\">\n            <a class=\"fill\" href=\"Portfolio\"  ><div class=\"fill banner-link\"><\/div><\/a>            \n   <div id=\"text-box-1337199462\" class=\"text-box banner-layer x50 md-x50 lg-x50 y50 md-y50 lg-y50 res-text\">\n                     <div data-animate=\"fadeInRight\">           <div class=\"text-box-content text dark text-shadow-5\">\n              \n              <div class=\"text-inner text-center\">\n                  \n<h3 class=\"uppercase\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>N\u1ec0N T\u1ea2NG HO\u1ea0T \u0110\u1ed8NG<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"lead\" style=\"text-align: left;\">1. C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0 d\u1eef li\u1ec7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng: \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ec5u n\u1ed9i dung (content) \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 thu th\u1eadp d\u1eef li\u1ec7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng, gi\u00fap Doanh nghi\u1ec7p x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 ch\u00e2n dung kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/p>\n<p class=\"lead\" style=\"text-align: left;\">2. S\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t n\u1ed9i dung: S\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o n\u1ed9i dung ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t, thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi t\u1eebng t\u1ec7p kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. V\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u00e1c n\u1ed9i dung truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng: Video (Viral Video, TVC, Review Video), status (text), \u1ea3nh, \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed9ng Gif, tranh v\u1ebd\u2026<\/p>\n<p class=\"lead\" style=\"text-align: left;\">3. H\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i n\u1ed9i dung: Gi\u00fap ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng m\u00f4t c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n              <\/div>\n           <\/div>\n       <\/div>                     \n<style>\n#text-box-1337199462 .text-inner {\n  padding: 0px 15px 0px 15px;\n}\n#text-box-1337199462 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n#text-box-1337199462 .text-box-content {\n  font-size: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n    <\/div>\n \n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n            \n<style>\n#banner-575302794 {\n  padding-top: 500px;\n}\n#banner-575302794 .bg.bg-loaded {\n  background-image: url(https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/achaumedia-banner-4.jpg);\n}\n#banner-575302794 .overlay {\n  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.21);\n}\n#banner-575302794 .ux-shape-divider--top svg {\n  height: 150px;\n  --divider-top-width: 100%;\n}\n#banner-575302794 .ux-shape-divider--bottom svg {\n  height: 150px;\n  --divider-width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n  <\/div>\n\n\n<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"col grid-col large-6 grid-col-1-3\" ><div class=\"col-inner\">\n\n  <div class=\"banner has-hover bg-zoom\" id=\"banner-1679024211\">\n          <div class=\"banner-inner fill\">\n        <div class=\"banner-bg fill\" >\n            <div class=\"bg fill bg-fill \"><\/div>\n                                    \n                    <\/div>\n\t\t\n        <div class=\"banner-layers container\">\n            <div class=\"fill banner-link\"><\/div>            \n   <div id=\"text-box-660259698\" class=\"text-box banner-layer x10 md-x10 lg-x10 y100 md-y100 lg-y100 res-text\">\n                     <div data-animate=\"fadeInUp\">           <div class=\"text-box-content text text-shadow-5\">\n              \n              <div class=\"text-inner text-left\">\n                  \n<h3 class=\"uppercase\"><strong>S\u1ee8 M\u1ec6NH C\u1ee6A \u00c1 CH\u00c2U MEDIA\u00a0<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"lead\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media l\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u, l\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng l\u00e0m t\u00f4n ch\u1ec9 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng. Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed v\u00e0 \u0111em l\u1ea1i gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb t\u1ed1i \u0111a cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng c\u00f9ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u&#8230;<\/p>\n              <\/div>\n           <\/div>\n       <\/div>                     \n<style>\n#text-box-660259698 {\n  width: 78%;\n}\n#text-box-660259698 .text-box-content {\n  font-size: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n    <\/div>\n \n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n            \n<style>\n#banner-1679024211 {\n  padding-top: 500px;\n}\n#banner-1679024211 .bg.bg-loaded {\n  background-image: url(https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/bg-meetDaikoPeople-1024x480.jpg);\n}\n#banner-1679024211 .ux-shape-divider--top svg {\n  height: 150px;\n  --divider-top-width: 100%;\n}\n#banner-1679024211 .ux-shape-divider--bottom svg {\n  height: 150px;\n  --divider-width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n  <\/div>\n\n\n<\/div><\/div>\n            <\/div>\n    <style>\n    #banner-grid-1693542942 .grid-col-1{height: 885px}\n    #banner-grid-1693542942 .grid-col-1-2{height: 442.5px}\n    #banner-grid-1693542942 .grid-col-1-3{height:295px}\n    #banner-grid-1693542942 .grid-col-2-3{height: 590px}\n    #banner-grid-1693542942 .grid-col-1-4{height: 221.25px}\n    #banner-grid-1693542942 .grid-col-3-4{height: 663.75px}\n\n\n    \n    \n\n  <\/style>\n    <\/div>\n  \n\t<section class=\"section\" id=\"section_1655115006\">\n\t\t<div class=\"bg section-bg fill bg-fill  bg-loaded\" >\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\t<div class=\"section-content relative\">\n\t\t\t\n<div class=\"container section-title-contain